Articles.Content:
Since the newest version of KSP Interstellar was released, an Unity crash always occurred when starting to load the GameData folder (starts with the alarm sound files).  KSP was installed with Steam.

Mods installed:

  • KSP Interstellar
  • KAS
  • EVE (including the excample config)
  • Making History
  • Breaking Ground
